<b>The Matter Involving Captain Koby</b>

4
00:00:08.780 --> 00:00:13.540
For centuries, our law has strictly
forbidden men from entering.

5
00:00:13.540 --> 00:00:17.960
We've nyever been invaded by men like this.

6
00:00:18.960 --> 00:00:23.420
Part of the mountain was destroyed,
and the town suffered heavy damage.

7
00:00:23.420 --> 00:00:27.010
If I remain here, the Marines will return.

8
00:00:27.010 --> 00:00:29.130
