17
00:01:12.470 --> 00:01:16.010
Deploy the new pacifista—
 the seraphim—to the front lines!

18
00:01:16.760 --> 00:01:19.020
Ensure the cameras are recording!

19
00:01:19.020 --> 00:01:20.230
Got it!

