77
00:01:26.400 --> 00:01:29.190
Warship spotted off the stern!

78
00:01:29.650 --> 00:01:32.700
Behind us! Pirates!

79
00:01:31.570 --> 00:01:32.700
Who is it?!

80
00:01:38.660 --> 00:01:42.290
Emperor Blackbeard's crew is here!

81
00:01:42.290 --> 00:01:43.670
Seaquake!

82
00:01:43.670 --> 00:01:46.090
The sea kings will notice!

83
00:01:51.880 --> 00:01:53.380
Who's that?!

84
00:01:53.380 --> 00:01:56.010
We can't fight a child!

85
00:01:56.010 --> 00:01:57.720
That's one strong kid!

86
00:01:57.720 --> 00:02:00.640
And don't you think she...?

87
00:02:12.070 --> 00:02:16.030
I've come for you, Pirate Empress!

88
00:02:21.080 --> 00:02:24.920
I won't let the Marines
have your devil fruit power!

89
00:02:26.330 --> 00:02:30.460
Hancock... That beautiful face...

90
00:02:30.460 --> 00:02:33.800
I wanna take her head
and make it my treasure.

91
00:02:33.800 --> 00:02:37.720
Do what you like after I've taken her power!

92
00:02:37.720 --> 00:02:39.220
C'mon!

93
00:02:39.220 --> 00:02:44.020
Shouldn't we take her alive
and have fun with her?

94
00:02:49.190 --> 00:02:52.240
Halt, Blackbeard Pirates!

95
00:02:53.030 --> 00:02:54.360
Vice Admiral Yamakaji!

96
00:02:54.360 --> 00:02:57.740
Give us the order to attack
Emperor Blackbeard!

97
00:02:57.740 --> 00:02:59.530
Wait for word from headquarters!

98
00:02:59.530 --> 00:03:00.410
What?!

99
00:03:01.240 --> 00:03:03.120
I have no business with you guys!

100
00:03:22.970 --> 00:03:24.430
Show yourself...

101
00:03:24.430 --> 00:03:27.440
Boa Hancock!

102
00:03:33.190 --> 00:03:34.740
Blackbeard!

103
00:03:34.740 --> 00:03:40.030
I guess it was inevitable that pirates
would try to capture the former Warlords!

104
00:03:41.870 --> 00:03:42.830
Damn!

105
00:03:46.500 --> 00:03:48.670
There's no end in sight!

106
00:03:48.670 --> 00:03:49.540
Watch out!

107
00:03:52.840 --> 00:03:54.380
I'm gonna die!

108
00:03:54.380 --> 00:03:55.630
Let's go.

109
00:03:55.630 --> 00:03:58.760
We've got to do something
about this situation first...

110
00:04:00.760 --> 00:04:02.510
Hancock!

111
00:04:02.510 --> 00:04:06.020
We, the Marines, would
prefer to avoid bloodshed!

112
00:04:06.020 --> 00:04:10.230
If you allow us to take you into custody,
you have my word we will withdraw!

113
00:04:12.020 --> 00:04:15.400
Don't be so cocky, Koby the Hero!

114
00:04:15.400 --> 00:04:18.150
Leave him to us, Big Sis!

115
00:04:18.570 --> 00:04:20.160
Preposterous.

116
00:04:20.780 --> 00:04:23.280
No one can capture me.

117
00:04:25.950 --> 00:04:28.290
I do not bow to anyone!

118
00:04:29.790 --> 00:04:31.040
Wait!

119
00:04:31.040 --> 00:04:33.040
No, Big Sis!

120
00:04:33.040 --> 00:04:36.170
Commodore Teach!
Nothing's working against hi–

121
00:04:41.680 --> 00:04:43.350
Hey, now...

122
00:04:43.350 --> 00:04:46.770
You all let one brat take you out?!

123
00:04:55.150 --> 00:04:57.690
Oh, you've gotta be kidding me...

124
00:04:57.690 --> 00:04:59.320
White hair.

125
00:04:59.700 --> 00:05:01.280
Brown skin.

126
00:05:01.700 --> 00:05:03.030
Black wings?!

127
00:05:21.800 --> 00:05:23.430
"PX"?!

128
00:05:27.140 --> 00:05:28.350
Don't tell me...

129
00:05:28.770 --> 00:05:30.230
he's a pacifista?!

130
00:05:57.800 --> 00:05:58.880
Damn!

131
00:05:58.880 --> 00:06:02.130
This brat is a pacifista?

132
00:06:02.130 --> 00:06:03.590
What's going on here?!

133
00:06:11.930 --> 00:06:13.600
This brat...

134
00:06:15.650 --> 00:06:16.980
is something else!

135
00:06:19.190 --> 00:06:21.990
Black Hole!

136
00:06:36.830 --> 00:06:39.960
Hey, this doesn't look good...

137
00:06:45.470 --> 00:06:47.050
– Hubba-hubba!
– Hubba-hubba!

138
00:06:47.050 --> 00:06:48.300
Wow!

139
00:06:48.300 --> 00:06:49.390
Hancock!

140
00:06:53.060 --> 00:06:55.440
The Blackbeard Pirates, too?!

141
00:06:58.400 --> 00:07:00.780
Slave Arrow!

142
00:07:08.070 --> 00:07:09.370
This is bad...

143
00:07:09.370 --> 00:07:11.740
We've got to go stop her, Helmeppo...

144
00:07:13.830 --> 00:07:15.370
Helmeppo!

145
00:07:16.120 --> 00:07:17.830
Vice Admiral Yamakaji!

146
00:07:19.670 --> 00:07:21.920
Pacifista! Wait!

147
00:07:31.970 --> 00:07:34.310
You'll shatter everyone who was petrified!

148
00:07:34.310 --> 00:07:35.520
Pacifista!

149
00:07:35.520 --> 00:07:37.980
This is an order! Stop!

150
00:07:38.850 --> 00:07:40.940
So that's Koby!

151
00:07:44.110 --> 00:07:45.610
Perfume...

152
00:07:48.780 --> 00:07:50.120
I can't dodge it!

153
00:07:51.200 --> 00:07:52.910
Black Vortex!

154
00:08:00.580 --> 00:08:03.670
How's that, Boa Hancock?

155
00:08:04.050 --> 00:08:08.430
My darkness absorbs devil fruit powers.

156
00:08:11.470 --> 00:08:16.180
<b>Emperor Marshall D. "Blackbeard" Teach
Bounty:    3.996 Billion</b>
<b>Former Warlord "Pirate Empress" Boa Hancock
Bounty:    1.659 Billion</b>

157
00:08:16.520 --> 00:08:18.060
Snake Princess!

158
00:08:18.060 --> 00:08:20.810
Her devil fruit power has been nullified!

159
00:08:21.440 --> 00:08:23.190
Unhand me...

160
00:08:23.190 --> 00:08:24.650
you filth.

161
00:08:24.650 --> 00:08:28.610
Well, there's the Pirate Empress
we all know and love!

162
00:08:29.030 --> 00:08:30.490
Good grief...

163
00:08:30.490 --> 00:08:34.330
All my stupid crew members
have been turned to stone!

164
00:08:36.290 --> 00:08:37.660
How should I proceed?

165
00:08:37.660 --> 00:08:40.790
Just as I thought, she's unimaginably tough!

166
00:08:40.790 --> 00:08:42.500
Boa Hancock!

167
00:08:42.500 --> 00:08:46.630
I've come for your power!

168
00:08:47.510 --> 00:08:50.930
This power is nothing without my beauty.

169
00:08:50.930 --> 00:08:55.060
If you kill me, your people
will remain petrified.

170
00:08:55.430 --> 00:08:58.560
The next user cannot undo it.

171
00:09:01.190 --> 00:09:03.400
We're getting nowhere.

172
00:09:03.400 --> 00:09:06.030
Koby the Hero!

173
00:09:06.030 --> 00:09:11.110
You did me a solid during
the Rocky Port Incident!

174
00:09:12.450 --> 00:09:16.370
Thanks to you, I was able
to take down Ochoku,

175
00:09:16.370 --> 00:09:20.000
and take his place as the boss of Pirate Island!

176
00:09:29.090 --> 00:09:30.970
So, Hero!

177
00:09:31.590 --> 00:09:35.680
If I take my hand off this wench,

178
00:09:35.680 --> 00:09:41.600
do you think she'll turn
my men back, just like that?

179
00:09:43.850 --> 00:09:47.940
She needs to change back our Marines, too!

180
00:09:48.570 --> 00:09:52.450
If you all agree to leave quietly…

181
00:09:53.490 --> 00:09:55.070
I'll do it!

182
00:09:56.240 --> 00:09:57.870
No.

183
00:09:57.870 --> 00:09:59.540
You're lying!

184
00:10:02.370 --> 00:10:06.960
If I unhand you, you'll petrify us.

185
00:10:06.960 --> 00:10:09.510
And that'll be it.

186
00:10:09.510 --> 00:10:11.010
Am I wrong?

187
00:10:15.550 --> 00:10:18.350
Frankly, it's hard to think of a man...

188
00:10:18.850 --> 00:10:23.890
who wouldn't fall victim
to that technique of yours.

189
00:10:25.730 --> 00:10:27.480
What should I do?

190
00:10:29.610 --> 00:10:31.780
I guess I should just kill you!

191
00:10:34.410 --> 00:10:36.160
Please, wait!

192
00:10:36.160 --> 00:10:38.780
Those losses would be too great!

193
00:10:53.090 --> 00:10:56.140
I knew the Marines would lay siege here...

194
00:10:58.680 --> 00:11:01.770
but to think it would reshape
the very island itself...

195
00:11:04.890 --> 00:11:07.350
D-Dark King Rayleigh!

196
00:11:08.400 --> 00:11:11.610
Sorry to keep you waiting, Hancock.

197
00:11:12.230 --> 00:11:13.650
Rayleigh...

198
00:11:16.200 --> 00:11:17.450
Hey.

199
00:11:17.450 --> 00:11:20.080
Whitebeard's little apprentice!

200
00:11:22.080 --> 00:11:27.210
I know it's childish to say this,
but I just don't like you!

201
00:11:35.050 --> 00:11:36.430
What?!

202
00:11:36.430 --> 00:11:39.720
That's the Silvers Rayleigh?!

203
00:11:49.810 --> 00:11:51.440
Hancock.

204
00:11:51.440 --> 00:11:54.150
Undo your petrification.

205
00:11:54.530 --> 00:11:56.530
I'll keep watch until the end.

206
00:11:57.030 --> 00:12:02.080
Nobody will try anything foolish.
Everyone will leave this island!

207
00:12:09.330 --> 00:12:11.000
<b>Present Day</b>

208
00:12:14.760 --> 00:12:16.340
I'm really glad...

209
00:12:16.760 --> 00:12:19.090
that you're alive.

210
00:12:21.300 --> 00:12:23.850
Thank you, Rayleigh.

211
