00:12:44.950 --> 00:12:48.960
the Calm Belts are no longer safe.

260
00:12:49.750 --> 00:12:51.880
The Marine siege.

261
00:12:51.880 --> 00:12:54.340
The introduction of these nyew weapons.

262
00:12:54.340 --> 00:12:56.960
Blackbeard's raid.

263
00:12:57.880 --> 00:13:01.090
I thought we were doomed...

264
00:13:08.230 --> 00:13:12.810
Frankly, I was only able to save you
due to the particulars of the situation.

265
00:13:15.270 --> 00:13:17.860
I've gotten old.

266
00:13:21.740 --> 00:13:27.290
Nowadays, I don't think I could
beat Blackbeard in a fight head-on.

267
00:13:28.950 --> 00:13:33.580
So the Marines thought those new weapons...

268
00:13:34.040 --> 00:13:39.360
could replace you guys, the Seven Warlords...

269
00:13:40.050 --> 00:13:42.550
In the end, those two...

270
00:13:42.550 --> 00:13:45.550
...got away without even a scratch!

271
00:13:45.550 --> 00:13:47.350
But the strange thing is...

272
00:13:47.890 --> 00:13:52.480
one of them looked just like our
big sister when she was a child.

273
00:13:58.190 --> 00:14:02.650
Aye aye. Proceeding directly
to the port of Egghead.

